    "en": {
      "title": "10-hour water cut in Colombo tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 10-hour water cut will be in place in several areas in Colombo on Saturday (20) from 11.00 pm to 9.00 am on Sunday (21) due to essential improvement improvement work, the National Water Supply and Drainage Board (NWSDB) said.",
        "As such, water supply to Colombo 5 and 6 will be interrupted while water supply will be at low pressure in Colombo 4.",
        "The NWSDB advises consumers to fill sufficient water ahead and expresses regret for the inconvenience caused. It also requests people to use water cautiotiously. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
